item.description: ### If you have troubles how to work with this, just take a shorter loot at this. I'll divide all these posts into 3 main steps you should do: 1. Upload File 2. Share File 3. Find an http:// link in response of Share File and Download Shared File --- ## Upload File: Send **PUT** request to the URL with adding a /FOLDER/filename.jpg You should include header **Content-Type: image/jpeg** (or anything accrding to file) and **Basic Auth** provided by **NEXTCLOUD ADMIN** If you get **201 Created**, proceed to the next URL --- ## Share File: Make the request above, adding Form inputs of **path** which we gave in URL while uploading into /FOLDER/filename.jpg Not forgetting about **Basic Auth** In response you'll get XML data, where you can find **https://...** within tags You can also get the and combine two these to get shareable link: _**https://.../download/filename.jpg**_
